{"_id":"1TZDcKSxEJJj32SX","name":"Akaviri Danger-Sense","permission":{"default":0,"xvA5SwRGJiyPsnxH":3},"type":"power","data":{"description":"<p>The character may make a Luck test in order to avoid surprise.</p>","dailyUse":false,"source":"","mpBonus":0,"hpBonus":0,"spBonus":0,"lpBonus":0,"wtBonus":0,"iniBonus":0,"speedBonus":0},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.7PWqlj7CsH2BIbg8"}},"img":"systems/uesrpg-d100/images/Icons/dangerSense.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"1njYOzZPlvWtttas","name":"Blessed Touch","permission":{"default":0,"xvA5SwRGJiyPsnxH":3},"type":"power","data":{"description":"<p>This character can speak the word of the divines for an hour in order to remove a single wound and all of its effects (not including lost limbs) from another character.</p>\n<p>This also restores an amount of HP equal to the damage dealt to cause the wound. The character may choose to burn 2d6 Luck in order to allow this power to also restore lost limbs. The target character must remain still for the entire duration while the character performs the ritual. This power can only be used once until the character&rsquo;s next long rest.</p>","dailyUse":false,"source":"","mpBonus":0,"hpBonus":0,"spBonus":0,"lpBonus":0,"wtBonus":0,"iniBonus":0,"speedBonus":0},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.7PWqlj7CsH2BIbg8"}},"img":"systems/uesrpg-d100/images/Icons/blessedTouch.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"3oBDq2qvfDzEPvKW","name":"Warmonger","permission":{"default":0,"xvA5SwRGJiyPsnxH":3},"type":"power","data":{"description":"<p>The character can spend a Stamina Point to automatically hit with a failed melee attack, with a minimum number of DoS equal to their Combat Style.</p>","dailyUse":false,"source":"The Warrior Stone","mpBonus":0,"hpBonus":0,"spBonus":0,"lpBonus":0,"wtBonus":0,"iniBonus":0,"speedBonus":0},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.7PWqlj7CsH2BIbg8"}},"img":"systems/uesrpg-d100/images/Icons/berserker.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"5n2cUocb2yAVUoN4","name":"Beast Tongue","permission":{"default":0,"xvA5SwRGJiyPsnxH":3},"type":"power","data":{"description":"<p>By preparing a short 5 minute ritual while outside among nature, a Bosmer can unleash a bit of their Wild Magic, allowing them to speak and understand animals. The GM can call for a Lore or Perception test to attempt to understand animals the character is not familiar with.</p>","dailyUse":false,"source":"","mpBonus":0,"hpBonus":0,"spBonus":0,"lpBonus":0,"wtBonus":0,"iniBonus":0,"speedBonus":0},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.7PWqlj7CsH2BIbg8"}},"img":"systems/uesrpg-d100/images/Icons/bestial.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"731QjHCxaY898qfT","name":"Trial and Error","permission":{"default":0,"xvA5SwRGJiyPsnxH":3},"type":"power","data":{"description":"<p>The character can spend a Stamina Point to reduce a Backfire roll by d6.</p>","dailyUse":false,"source":"The Apprentice Stone","mpBonus":0,"hpBonus":0,"spBonus":0,"lpBonus":0,"wtBonus":0,"iniBonus":0,"speedBonus":0},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.7PWqlj7CsH2BIbg8"}},"img":"systems/uesrpg-d100/images/Icons/expert.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"CUYYniLMNjBB7LgK","name":"Shadowmeld","permission":{"default":0,"xvA5SwRGJiyPsnxH":3},"type":"power","data":{"description":"<p>The character can spend a Stamina Point to become Invisible for one Round. Performing Attacks or casting spells breaks the invsibility immediately.</p>","dailyUse":false,"source":"The Shadow Stone","mpBonus":0,"hpBonus":0,"spBonus":0,"lpBonus":0,"wtBonus":0,"iniBonus":0,"speedBonus":0},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.7PWqlj7CsH2BIbg8"}},"img":"systems/uesrpg-d100/images/Icons/blending.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"CnMiSGkbMCFjSI9d","name":"Dark Ritual","permission":{"default":0,"xvA5SwRGJiyPsnxH":3},"type":"power","data":{"description":"<p>The character can, once per Long Rest, spend a Stamina Point to reanimate a number of corpses as Zombies or skeletons as Skeletons up to their Willpower Bonus for one minute within 10m of the character. These undead are not directly controlled by the character but will not harm them or their allies.</p>","dailyUse":false,"source":"The Ritual Stone","mpBonus":0,"hpBonus":0,"spBonus":0,"lpBonus":0,"wtBonus":0,"iniBonus":0,"speedBonus":0},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.7PWqlj7CsH2BIbg8"}},"img":"systems/uesrpg-d100/images/Icons/darkRitual.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"F7akGz7fmeJj5Iaa","name":"Mara's Gift","permission":{"default":0,"xvA5SwRGJiyPsnxH":3},"type":"power","data":{"description":"<p>This character can speak the word of the divines for an hour in order to remove a single wound and all of its effects (not including lost limbs) from themselves. This also restores an amount of HP equal to the amount of damage dealt to cause the wound. The character may choose to burn 2d6 Luck in order to allow this power to also restore lost limbs. This power can only be used once until after the character&rsquo;s next long rest.</p>","dailyUse":false,"source":"","mpBonus":0,"hpBonus":0,"spBonus":0,"lpBonus":0,"wtBonus":0,"iniBonus":0,"speedBonus":0},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.7PWqlj7CsH2BIbg8"}},"img":"systems/uesrpg-d100/images/Icons/marasGift.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"HjjhvdNyo4ErW1jV","name":"Lover's Kiss","permission":{"default":0,"xvA5SwRGJiyPsnxH":3},"type":"power","data":{"description":"<p>The character can spend a Stamina Point to force a target at Touch range to test Willpower at +0 as a Secondary Action. If the target fails, they automatically fail the next attack or defensive reaction they attempt.</p>","dailyUse":false,"source":"The Lover Stone","mpBonus":0,"hpBonus":0,"spBonus":0,"lpBonus":0,"wtBonus":0,"iniBonus":0,"speedBonus":0},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.7PWqlj7CsH2BIbg8"}},"img":"systems/uesrpg-d100/images/Icons/loversKiss.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"M0rINatw3BFEi6xR","name":"Trollblood","permission":{"default":0,"xvA5SwRGJiyPsnxH":3},"type":"power","data":{"description":"<p>The character can spend a Stamina Point to regain 3 Hit Points as a free action.</p>","dailyUse":false,"source":"The Lord Stone","mpBonus":0,"hpBonus":0,"spBonus":0,"lpBonus":0,"wtBonus":0,"iniBonus":0,"speedBonus":0},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.7PWqlj7CsH2BIbg8"}},"img":"systems/uesrpg-d100/images/Icons/regeneration.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"PFB0tXTv36ELZAh0","name":"Improved Sprint","permission":{"default":0,"xvA5SwRGJiyPsnxH":3},"type":"power","data":{"description":"<p>The character increases their Speed by 1. Additionally, when the character spends a Stamina Point to Sprint, they instead move three times their Speed.</p>","dailyUse":false,"source":"The Steed Stone","mpBonus":0,"hpBonus":0,"spBonus":0,"lpBonus":0,"wtBonus":0,"iniBonus":0,"speedBonus":1},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.7PWqlj7CsH2BIbg8"}},"img":"systems/uesrpg-d100/images/Icons/lightningReflexes.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"Z6PHNRjviMZ5QTiL","name":"Moonshadow","permission":{"default":0,"xvA5SwRGJiyPsnxH":3},"type":"power","data":{"description":"<p>The character possesses a simple form of innate shadow magic. This power may be activated once a day with the use of the Cast Magic action.</p>\n<p>The character becomes Invisible for 18 seconds (3 rounds). The character may spend a Luck point, or burn one Luck, to extend this duration by one round (this may be done as many times as the character desires). This power may only be used once until after the character&rsquo;s next long rest. The effect is broken if they make an attack, but reactivates at the beginning of their next round as long as they still have time left.</p>","dailyUse":false,"source":"","mpBonus":0,"hpBonus":0,"spBonus":0,"lpBonus":0,"wtBonus":0,"iniBonus":0,"speedBonus":0},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.7PWqlj7CsH2BIbg8"}},"img":"systems/uesrpg-d100/images/Icons/invisible.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"ZtKDG5E8A1YiVbBb","name":"Treasure Seeker","permission":{"default":0,"xvA5SwRGJiyPsnxH":3},"type":"power","data":{"description":"<p>The character has a knack for finding treasure, and overcoming the obstacles that protect it. At any time the character can choose to reroll a failed Subterfuge test made to pick a lock or disarm a trap, but only once for a given test. This power may only be used once until after the character&rsquo;s next long rest.</p>","dailyUse":false,"source":"","mpBonus":0,"hpBonus":0,"spBonus":0,"lpBonus":0,"wtBonus":0,"iniBonus":0,"speedBonus":0},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.7PWqlj7CsH2BIbg8"}},"img":"systems/uesrpg-d100/images/Icons/businessman.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"cKArj9POPihEYqRS","name":"Beggar's Nose","permission":{"default":0,"xvA5SwRGJiyPsnxH":3},"type":"power","data":{"description":"<p>The character can spend a Stamina Point to turn a failed Observe, Navigate, or Survival test into a successful test, scoring a minimum DoS equal to the character&rsquo;s skill rank.</p>","dailyUse":false,"source":"The Tower Stone","mpBonus":0,"hpBonus":0,"spBonus":0,"lpBonus":0,"wtBonus":0,"iniBonus":0,"speedBonus":0},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.7PWqlj7CsH2BIbg8"}},"img":"systems/uesrpg-d100/images/Icons/honedSenses.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"cUztIuM7MnIE9YBH","name":"Ancestor Guardian","permission":{"default":0,"xvA5SwRGJiyPsnxH":3},"type":"power","data":{"description":"<p>Once per Long Rest as a Free Action, the character can cast Sanctuary (3) on themselves that lasts for 3 Rounds. It costs no Magicka Points and requires no test. They may also perform a ritual that costs 10 Septims worth of incense to consult with an ancestor, asking up to 1d4+1 questions. The Ancestor can reply with a disembodied voice only the character can hear or sends imagery and signs to be interpreted.</p>","dailyUse":false,"source":"","mpBonus":0,"hpBonus":0,"spBonus":0,"lpBonus":0,"wtBonus":0,"iniBonus":0,"speedBonus":0},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.7PWqlj7CsH2BIbg8"}},"img":"systems/uesrpg-d100/images/Icons/fearless.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"dVPzaNlBKuc7HDKN","name":"Sorcerous Chant","permission":{"default":0,"xvA5SwRGJiyPsnxH":3},"type":"power","data":{"description":"<p>The character can spend a Stamina Point to reduce the casting penalty of a spell that is a higher spell level than the caster&rsquo;s School rank by +10.</p>","dailyUse":false,"source":"The Mage Stone","mpBonus":0,"hpBonus":0,"spBonus":0,"lpBonus":0,"wtBonus":0,"iniBonus":0,"speedBonus":0},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.7PWqlj7CsH2BIbg8"}},"img":"systems/uesrpg-d100/images/Icons/sorcerousChant.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"eMCUq4jo0MKZ9ATd","name":"Magic Eater","permission":{"default":0,"xvA5SwRGJiyPsnxH":3},"type":"power","data":{"description":"<p>The character can spend a Stamina Point to increase their Resistance (Magic) by 2 points for one Round as a free action.</p>","dailyUse":false,"source":"The Atronach Stone","mpBonus":0,"hpBonus":0,"spBonus":0,"lpBonus":0,"wtBonus":0,"iniBonus":0,"speedBonus":0},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.7PWqlj7CsH2BIbg8"}},"img":"systems/uesrpg-d100/images/Icons/magicEater.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"jpglLVQNVdxCYu29","name":"Adrenaline Rush","permission":{"default":0,"xvA5SwRGJiyPsnxH":3},"type":"power","data":{"description":"<p>The character may choose to gain 1 SP at any time. If the character is fatigued when this power is used then remove a level of fatigue instead. This SP per-sists only for that encounter, and this power may only be used once until after the character&rsquo;s next long rest.</p>","dailyUse":false,"source":"","mpBonus":0,"hpBonus":0,"spBonus":0,"lpBonus":0,"wtBonus":0,"iniBonus":0,"speedBonus":0},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.7PWqlj7CsH2BIbg8"}},"img":"systems/uesrpg-d100/images/Icons/champion.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"nqNWiQmlH3UFlSZU","name":"Lady's Blessing","permission":{"default":0,"xvA5SwRGJiyPsnxH":3},"type":"power","data":{"description":"<p>The character regenerates one additional Stamina Point during Short Rests.</p>","dailyUse":false,"source":"The Lady Stone","mpBonus":0,"hpBonus":0,"spBonus":0,"lpBonus":0,"wtBonus":0,"iniBonus":0,"speedBonus":0},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.7PWqlj7CsH2BIbg8"}},"img":"systems/uesrpg-d100/images/Icons/skill_134.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"ojgcYhknzOQGr7Bz","name":"War Cry","permission":{"default":0,"xvA5SwRGJiyPsnxH":3},"type":"power","data":{"description":"<p>The character is able to call on a very simple form of the Thu&rsquo;um and harness it to frighten their enemies in battle. As free action, they can issue a mighty war cry that forces all enemies who hear it to make a Panic (+20) test. If a character passes this test, they are immune to the effects of this power for the remainder of the encounter. This power may only be used once until after the character&rsquo;s next long rest.</p>","dailyUse":false,"source":"","mpBonus":0,"hpBonus":0,"spBonus":0,"lpBonus":0,"wtBonus":0,"iniBonus":0,"speedBonus":0},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.7PWqlj7CsH2BIbg8"}},"img":"systems/uesrpg-d100/images/Icons/berserker.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"q3JDZO27J3533of2","name":"Blessed Word","permission":{"default":0,"xvA5SwRGJiyPsnxH":3},"type":"power","data":{"description":"<p>The character may begin speaking the word of the divines through the use of the Cast Magic action. This creates a circle with a radius equal to their Willpower bonus in meters. Characters with the Undead or Undying traits must flee the circle and no characters with those traits may willingly enter it unless they can pass a -40 Willpower test (which may be attempted once per round).</p>","dailyUse":false,"source":"","mpBonus":0,"hpBonus":0,"spBonus":0,"lpBonus":0,"wtBonus":0,"iniBonus":0,"speedBonus":0},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.7PWqlj7CsH2BIbg8"}},"img":"systems/uesrpg-d100/images/Icons/blessedTouch.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"qHIx6mhn6TyMm7aH","name":"Bend Luck","permission":{"default":0,"xvA5SwRGJiyPsnxH":3},"type":"power","data":{"description":"<p>The character can spend a Stamina Point to immediately make a Luck test. If they pass, the character gains +1 Luck Point this session immediately. If they fail, they lose 1 Luck Point this session. If the character has no Luck Points remaining when they fail, Burn 1 Luck instead.</p>","dailyUse":false,"source":"The Serpent Stone","mpBonus":0,"hpBonus":0,"spBonus":0,"lpBonus":0,"wtBonus":0,"iniBonus":0,"speedBonus":0},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.7PWqlj7CsH2BIbg8"}},"img":"systems/uesrpg-d100/images/Icons/bendLuck.png","effects":[]}
